name: Korto Maltese generative series 1 - Powerd by Manifold

metadata.name: Sneakers Generative art S1.P8
metadata.description:
A collaboration Artist Machine  
I'm an artist immersed in streetwear culture.  
I'm exploring AI generative art. For this series I used Dall.E2 to initiate the first piece, from there I work on the first piece generated and collaborate with the machine to develop variants… I continue the process of collaboration artist-machine with the variants until I’m happy with the piece.
